svg.text: Stickers: Decorate your photos with unexpected stickersGet back to fun school days with digital stickers! Enter “stickers” in the search box of our image library and choose from a variety of eccentric slogans and innocent stamps that you can drag into your collages and photos on social networks. Decorate the photo of your loved one with a sticker and show that you can’t think of anyone else, or animate the collage of photos of the trip with funny winged phrases and sayings.
